STEP 4: Else, print "n2 is greater than n1"
STEP 5: End

ASSIGNMENT 19: Check whether it is head or tail
ALGORITHM:
STEP 1: Start
STEP 2: Input toss value c
STEP 3: If c == 'H' or c == 'h', print "It is a head"
STEP 4: If c == 'T' or c == 't', print "It is a tail"
STEP 5: End

