STEP 4: Else, print "It is not a whole number"
STEP 5: End

ASSIGNMENT 21: Check leap year using ladder if-else
ALGORITHM:
STEP 1: Start
STEP 2: Input year y
STEP 3: If y % 400 == 0, print "Leap year"
STEP 4: Else if y % 100 == 0, print "Not a Leap year"
STEP 5: Else if y % 4 == 0, print "Leap year"
STEP 6: Else, print "Not a Leap year"
STEP 7: End

ASSIGNMENT 22: Maximum among three numbers using ladder if-else
ALGORITHM:
STEP 1: Start
STEP 2: Input three numbers a, b, c
STEP 3: If a > b and a > c, print "a is the greatest number"
STEP 4: Else if b > a and b > c, print "b is the greatest number"
STEP 5: Else, print "c is the greatest number"
STEP 6: End

ASSIGNMENT 23: Check if a letter is vowel or consonant
ALGORITHM:
STEP 1: Start
STEP 2: Input a letter l
STEP 3: If l is 'a','e','i','o','u' (or uppercase), print "Letter is vowel"
STEP 4: Else, print "Letter is consonant"
STEP 5: End

